aised by men, and believes not in God and the Last Day: for his parable is that of a smooth rock with [a little] earth upon it - and then a rainstorm smites it and leaves it hard and bare. Such as these shall have no gain whatever from all their [good] works: for God does not guide people who refuse to acknowledge the truth.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/271.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":87495,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87496,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87497,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87498,"position":4,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87499,"position":5,"arabic":"تُبْطِلُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা নষ্ট করো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87500,"position":6,"arabic":"صَدَقَـٰتِكُم","translation":"তোমাদের দান সমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87501,"position":7,"arabic":"بِٱلْمَنِّ","translation":"(অনুগ্রহ প্রদানের) খোটা দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87502,"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَذَىٰ","translation":"ও কষ্ট (দিয়ে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87503,"position":9,"arabic":"كَٱلَّذِى","translation":"(ঐ ব্যক্তির) মতো যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87504,"position":10,"arabic":"يُنفِقُ","translation":"ব্যয় করে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87505,"position":11,"arabic":"مَالَهُۥ","translation":"তার ধন সম্পদ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87506,"position":12,"arabic":"رِئَآءَ","translation":"দেখানোর জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/002_264_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id